text: Aa is a genus of orchids. This genus' peculiar name was created in order to make it always appear at the top of alphabetical lists. Species (according to Kew): * Aa achalensis * Aa argyrolepis * Aa aurantiaca * Aa calceata * Aa colombiana - paper orchid * Aa denticulata * Aa erosa * Aa fiebrigii * Aa figueroi * Aa hieronymi * Aa lehmannii * Aa leucantha * Aa lorentzii * Aa lozanoi * Aa macra * Aa maderoi * Aa mandonii * Aa matthewsii * Aa microtidis * Aa paleacea * Aa riobambae * Aa rosei * Aa schickendanzii * Aa sphaeroglossa * Aa trilobulata * Aa weddelliana == Gallery == === Aa argyrolepis === === Aa calceata === === Aa maderoi === Category:Orchids
